Package com.artisan.incodeapi

Class Summary
ArtisanExperimentManager Manages all in-code experiments designed for use with Artisan.
ArtisanProfileManager ArtisanProfileManager is a singleton that is automatically initialized when your app starts.
ArtisanPurchaseWorkflowManager Manages a purchase workflow with Artisan.
ArtisanSocialSharingManager Manages tracking social sharing events with Artisan.

This includes recording Artisan analytics events for each share to a social network along with any additional information that you would like to track.

These analytics events are automatically synced with Artisan and can be used for Advanced segmentation and personalization with the Artisan analytics reports, experiments, power hooks and campaigns.
ArtisanTrackingManager Manages in-code analytics tracking designed for use with Artisan.
InCodeExperimentDetails An object containing useful information about an in-code experiment These are retrieved via the `ArtisanExperimentManager#getInCodeExperimentDetails` method
